PPF Group Bought Sazka Debt From Billionaire Vitek, CTK Reports

-- B y   L a d k a   B a u e r o v a
-- 
2011-03-21T16:38:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-21/ppf-group-bought-sazka-debt-from-billionaire-vitek-ctk-reports.html
PPF Group NV, the  Czech Republic ’s
largest closely held financial company, bought lottery provider
Sazka AS’s debt from billionaire Radovan Vitek,  CTK  reported,
without saying where it got the information.  Sazka AS is in insolvency proceedings and has stopped
paying winnings.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ladka Bauerova in Prague at 
 lbauerova@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Douglas Lytle at 
 dlytle@bloomberg.net . 